blog_text: Rumi Neely's Fashion Toast, was probably the first fashion blog I stumbled upon when blogging wasn't even a thing yet back in '09...Rumi has since taken her cool girl LA style and designed a clothing line "for the girls who get it." We get it and we love it. Shop our edit.
